OL,3,CCharity set up to tackle Guernsey's
OL,4,C'significant hidden homeless problem'
OL,6,Ffirst charity "dedicated to ending
OL,7,Fhomelessness" has been set up.
OL,9,F'At Home in Guernsey' will support
OL,10,Fpeople who are homeless or at risk of
OL,11,Fbecoming homeless, including 'sofa-
OL,12,Fsurfers' living temporarily with other
OL,13,Fhouseholds.
OL,15,FJim Roberts has been heavily involved
OL,16,Fin creating the charity and says the
OL,17,Fteam will work to provide a more
OL,18,Faccurate picture of the number of
OL,19,Fhomeless people in the island.
