OL,6,FHe said: "The closest thing we've got
OL,7,Fis a count of people who are
OL,8,Finsecurely housed.
OL,10,F"That's people in B&B's and lodging
OL,11,Fhouses and people who have moved
OL,12,Faddress frequently in a year.
OL,14,F"So by the States own reckoning
OL,15,Fthere's over 1,000 people in that
OL,16,Fsituation."
