OL,3,CCharity set up to tackle Guernsey's
OL,4,C'significant hidden homeless problem'
OL,6,FThe Foundation's Chair Sir Richard
OL,7,FCollas explained there was a "need for
OL,8,Fa charity focused on helping the many
OL,9,Fpeople who find themselves without
OL,10,Fsecure accommodation."
OL,12,FThe charity has been guaranteed
OL,13,Ffunding for the next three years by
OL,14,FSpecsavers.
OL,16,FThe company's Chief Executive John
OL,17,FPerkins said: "The uncomfortable truth
OL,18,Fis that Guernsey has a significant
OL,19,Fhidden homeless problem, which as a
OL,20,Fcommunity we need to do all we can to
OL,21,Fsupport."
